title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H1 - Oct 1 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H1 - Oct 1 2022
description:
Is the right's win in Italy a harbinger for our midterms? Fetterman fails to complete a sentence on the Eagles and Steelers. Biden's FBI raids the home of a pro-life activist in Pennsylvania, but no time to investigate Hunter Biden or rampant crime all over America. Lindsey Graham's abortion bill. Will big news stories freeze the midterms?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
